          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Keeping Families Home Act of</b> <b>2017</b></p> <p>This bill directs certain mortgage servicers to establish deed-for-lease programs that allow eligible mortgagors,&nbsp;in lieu of foreclosure agreements, to remain in their homes as renters.</p>]]></text>
